00:19:47.760 --> 00:19:50.860
of intellectual property,
and he also writes a really,

00:19:50.860 --> 00:19:54.330
really good blog so you should
check it out at lawtheories.com.

00:19:54.330 --> 00:19:58.510
So Devlin, why don't
