00:27:27.810 --> 00:27:29.510
Hey, everybody.

00:27:29.510 --> 00:27:31.550
My name is Joseph Gordon-Levitt.

00:27:31.550 --> 00:27:35.990
I work in movies and TV,

00:27:35.990 --> 00:27:38.920
and I also started a
company called HITRECORD.

00:27:38.920 --> 00:27:41.240
It's an online community
