I've heard from many people
say they're not creative.

00:46:02.120 --> 00:46:02.680
But we're going to try

00:46:02.680 --> 00:46:04.620
and actually do something
real quick here.

00:46:04.620 --> 00:46:08.580
First of all, I'm
going to surprise her

00:46:08.580 --> 00:46:11.410
and take a picture
with the Register.

00:46:11.410 --> 00:46:11.960
All right.

00:46:11.960 --> 00:46:16.840
So we're creating a
photograph together.

00:46:16.840 --> 00:46:19.000
Now, this is the
riskiest part of all.

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:22.090
I'm going to ask that
you guys do something

00:46:22.090 --> 00:46:23.400
that you were not
prepared to do today,

00:46:23.400 --> 00:46:24.730
and I'm going to record it.

