00:46:42.360 --> 00:46:44.480
so it's hard to say yes, right?

00:46:44.480 --> 00:46:46.260
So join me in clapping.

00:46:46.260 --> 00:46:48.510
Okay, ready?

00:46:48.510 --> 00:47:02.040
[ Clapping ]

