Right now, we have
taken a photograph.

00:47:05.670 --> 00:47:08.210
We have just made a
video on my Snapchat.

00:47:08.210 --> 00:47:09.330
You don't even know
what that is yet,

00:47:09.330 --> 00:47:11.000
but we made a video together.

00:47:11.000 --> 00:47:12.470
We collaborated.

00:47:12.470 --> 00:47:17.260
This is how creators
are working these days.

00:47:17.260 --> 00:47:18.870
In terms that used to be --

00:47:18.870 --> 00:47:20.020
that's not the only
way they're working,

00:47:20.020 --> 00:47:23.190
but these are just new
ways that we're working.

00:47:23.190 --> 00:47:25.850
So in, say, a film production,

00:47:25.850 --> 00:47:29.770
those schedules are
weeks, months, years.

00:47:29.770 --> 00:47:35.020
The new schedule for creators
are minutes, hours, days.

00:47:35.020 --> 00:47:37.950
And the laws that we have,
they don't address that.

00:47:37.950 --> 00:47:41.920
Now you can be saying -- that's
just -- this is just child play.

00:47:41.920 --> 00:47:45.200
Snapchat is a thing that
my 14-year-old uses.

00:47:45.200 --> 00:47:48.120
I could get paid a
lot of money for this.

00:47:48.120 --> 00:47:49.150
And people do.

00:47:49.150 --> 00:47:51.850
10, 20, 25 grand.

00:47:51.850 --> 00:47:53.590
I don't think there's
a person in this room

00:47:53.590 --> 00:47:56.230
who wouldn't want 25 grand
for creating the thing

00:47:56.230 --> 00:47:58.190
that we just created together.

00:47:58.190 --> 00:48:01.220
So my point is that
things are different.

00:48:01.220 --> 00:48:05.410
And we need laws, and we need
mentality that can address it.

00:48:05.410 --> 00:48:06.970
So that's point two.

00:48:06.970 --> 00:48:11.120
And point three is that
we all have real reach.

00:48:11.120 --> 00:48:14.990
I'm going to push that thing
out, whether you like it or not,

00:48:14.990 --> 00:48:17.080
to two million people.

