Obama doesn't care
about that stuff.

00:48:41.750 --> 00:48:43.860
Regardless of what side
of the aisle you're on,

00:48:43.860 --> 00:48:46.550
I had the good fortune of
being with Vice President Biden

00:48:46.550 --> 00:48:51.020
and some other influencers,
whatever that term mean.

00:48:51.020 --> 00:48:53.780
And they were YouTube
influencers,

00:48:53.780 --> 00:48:56.730
and Biden made a
really important point.

00:48:56.730 --> 00:48:59.480
And that point was,
hey, a couple weeks ago,

00:48:59.480 --> 00:49:02.070
I was at the Oscars,
and I made a speech

00:49:02.070 --> 00:49:07.620
about the campaign called
"It's On Us," ending assault

00:49:07.620 --> 00:49:10.950
on women and vulnerable men.

00:49:10.950 --> 00:49:14.860
And it's a very powerful
campaign that I'm very proud

00:49:14.860 --> 00:49:17.640
to be a part of, but he said
something to the eight of us,

00:49:17.640 --> 00:49:19.980
it was really -- it struck me.

00:49:19.980 --> 00:49:22.970
It was like, "I was on Oscars,
and the reach of that is

00:49:22.970 --> 00:49:25.790
about 30 million people."

00:49:25.790 --> 00:49:27.800
The audience that we
have collected here

00:49:27.800 --> 00:49:30.680
in this room today, the eight
of you, you have a reach

00:49:30.680 --> 00:49:35.350
of 40 million people
on a daily basis.

00:49:35.350 --> 00:49:39.010
So what we are doing is
we are sharing at scale,

00:49:39.010 --> 00:49:44.720
without permission, differently,
faster, I would say,

00:49:44.720 --> 00:49:47.890
more effectively,
than ever before.

00:49:47.890 --> 00:49:50.220
So, I promised a
five paragraph essay.

00:49:50.220 --> 00:49:51.120
I told you what I was
going to tell you.

00:49:51.120 --> 00:49:54.550
I'm telling you these three
points, and now I'm very,

00:49:54.550 --> 00:49:56.780
very excited to sit down
here and talk with my sort

00:49:56.780 --> 00:50:00.720
of esteemed colleagues about
what the future of creativity,

00:50:00.720 --> 00:50:02.520
specifically, digital
creativity,

00:50:02.520 --> 00:50:04.390
means and how it's different.

